<script>
	export default {
		data() {
			return {
				content: `<div><div class="lake-content-editor-core lake-engine" data-lake-element="root"><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;">为提升小程序开发者接入体验，目前支付宝小程序通过 JSAPI 的方式可以直接获取用户信息，产品上可以提供更加统一的支付宝小程序产品体验，技术上可以减少开发者对接支付宝网关的成本（使用这种方式不需要调用 openapi.alipay.com 这个网关进行信息获取）。</p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;">不同于现有的<a href="https://opendocs.alipay.com/mini/introduce/twn8vq" target="_blank">获取会员基础信息</a>功能，该功能的权限需要单独申请使用。</p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><h1 id="IaHW2" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;">第一步：创建小程序<span class="doc-anchor-wrapper" data-heading="H1" data-hash="%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F"><span class="doc-anchor" id="%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F"></span></span></h1><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;">要在您的小程序内使用“获取会员身份信息”功能，您需要首先完成<a href="https://opendocs.alipay.com/mini/introduce/register" target="_blank">开发者入驻</a>并<a href="https://opendocs.alipay.com/mini/introduce/create" target="_blank">创建小程序</a>。</p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><h1 id="sqgzah" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;">第二步：添加功能并签约<span class="doc-anchor-wrapper" data-heading="H1" data-hash="%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%B9%B6%E7%AD%BE%E7%BA%A6"><span class="doc-anchor" id="%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%B9%B6%E7%AD%BE%E7%BA%A6"></span></span></h1><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><span>小程序创建完成后，开发者在&nbsp;</span><strong>功能列表</strong>&nbsp;部分可以点击&nbsp;<strong>添加功能</strong><span>&nbsp;来添加&nbsp;</span><strong>获取会员身份信息&nbsp;</strong><span>功能。</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;">“获取会员身份信息”功能需要点击 <strong>用户信息申请</strong> 后才能生效；完成申请后，需要一个工作日左右的审核时间<span>（审批结果会以短信和邮件形式告知）</span>，待审核完毕后，功能的状态会变成“已生效”，即可使用“获取会员身份信息”功能。</p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><strong>说明：</strong></p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><span>“获取会员身份信息”功能包的添加方式与“获取会员手机号”的添加功能方式</span></p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><h1 id="i6c5sd" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;"><a href="20180927112538811599/quickstart/edit#i6c5sd"></a>第三步：安全配置<span class="doc-anchor-wrapper" data-heading="H1" data-hash="%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE"><span class="doc-anchor" id="%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE"></span></span></h1><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;">按照支付宝数据安全规范，明文的敏感数据不允许在前端露出。通过 jsApi 获取信息时若涉及敏感数据支付宝会对返回的报文进行加密或者签名，需要小程序开发者在开发者中心配置签名算法和 AES 密钥。详细可参考 <a href="20180927112538811599/jsapi" target="_blank">JSAPI&nbsp;加密加签说明</a>。</p><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><h1 id="tnkygg" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;"><a href="20180927112538811599/quickstart/edit#tnkygg"></a>第四步：配置授权组件<span class="doc-anchor-wrapper" data-heading="H1" data-hash="%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6"><span class="doc-anchor" id="%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6"></span></span></h1><h2 id="7t2wqz" style="padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;"><a href="20180927112538811599/quickstart/edit#7t2wqz"></a>小程序前端代码<span class="doc-anchor-wrapper" data-heading="H2" data-hash="%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81"><span class="doc-anchor" id="%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81"></span></span></h2><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><div data-card-type="block" data-lake-card="codeblock" id="f48ea600"><pre class="cm-s-default"><span class="docs-code-copy" data-clipboard-snippet="null"></span><code><span class="cm-tag cm-bracket" style="color: rgb(34, 134, 58); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">&lt;</span><span class="cm-tag" style="color: rgb(34, 134, 58); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">button</span> <span class="cm-attribute" style="color: rgb(111, 66, 193); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">open-type</span>=<span class="cm-string" style="color: rgb(102, 153, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">"getAuthorize"</span> <span class="cm-attribute" style="color: rgb(111, 66, 193); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">onGetAuthorize</span>=<span class="cm-string" style="color: rgb(102, 153, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">"onGetAuthorize"</span> 
						<span class="cm-attribute" style="color: rgb(111, 66, 193); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">onError</span>=<span class="cm-string" style="color: rgb(102, 153, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">"onAuthError"</span> <span class="cm-attribute" style="color: rgb(111, 66, 193); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">scope</span>=<span class="cm-string" style="color: rgb(102, 153, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">'userInfo'</span><span class="cm-tag cm-bracket" style="color: rgb(34, 134, 58); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">&gt;</span>
							用户公开信息授权
						<span class="cm-tag cm-bracket" style="color: rgb(34, 134, 58); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">&lt;/</span><span class="cm-tag" style="color: rgb(34, 134, 58); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">button</span><span class="cm-tag cm-bracket" style="color: rgb(34, 134, 58); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">&gt;</span></code></pre></div><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;"><br></p><ul lake-indent="0" style="list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;"><li><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;">属性说明</p></li></ul><div data-card-type="block" data-lake-card="table" id="eb9e9182"><div class="xe-table-wrapper"><table class="lake-table" style="width: 753px; outline: none; border-collapse: collapse;"><colgroup><col width="377" span="1"><col width="377" span="1"></colgroup><tbody><tr style="height: 33px;"><td style="min-width: 90px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: 1px solid rgb(217, 217, 217); padding: 4px 8px; cursor: default;"><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;">属性</p></td><td style="min-width: 90px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word; border: 1px solid rgb(217, 217, 217); padding: 4px 8px; cursor: default;"><p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 24px;